ent-AnomalyScanner-name = anomaly scanner
ent-AnomalyScanner-desc = A hand-held scanner built to collect information on various anomalous objects.
ent-AnomalyLocatorUnpowered-name = anomaly locator
ent-AnomalyLocatorUnpowered-desc = A device designed to aid in the locating of anomalies. Did you check the gas miners?
ent-AnomalyLocatorWideUnpowered-name = wide-spectrum anomaly locator
ent-AnomalyLocatorWideUnpowered-desc = A device that looks for anomalies from an extended distance, but has no way to determine the distance to them.
ent-WeaponGauntletGorilla-name = G.O.R.I.L.L.A. gauntlet
ent-WeaponGauntletGorilla-desc = A robust piece of research equipment. When powered with an anomaly core, a single blow can launch anomalous objects through the air.
